{"tid":773404,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"白宮擬移除海航在紐約的一處地產大樓產權","createTime":"2018-08-09T13:11:33.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-09T16:58:43.000Z","uid":13663,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"62f852b578977a24255d5fe89d5b6751a48f74a5","tid":773404,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:11:33.000Z","msg":"白宮擬移除海航在紐約的一處地產大樓產權<br />\n最後更新 {0} 2018年8月9日<br />\n美國之音<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://gdb.voanews.com/F95F8DE6-C7E1-4A5F-BFF5-6F0291D8EE50_w408_r1_s.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgdb.voanews.com%2FF95F8DE6-C7E1-4A5F-BFF5-6F0291D8EE50_w408_r1_s.jpg&h=6733152b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n位於紐約市曼哈頓區第三大道的紐約海航大廈 (美國之音章真拍攝)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n華盛頓 &mdash; <br />\n據《紐約郵報》(New York Post)星期三晚報導，川普政府以具體國家安全理由，準備採取行動迫使中國海航公司轉手紐約一棟地產大樓的多數股份。<span style=\"color: red;\">這將是美國國會8月1日為美國外國投資委員會擴權，增加審查外國房地產投資權限後，川普政府採取的首次行動</span>。<br />\n<br />\n海航公司佔有多數股份的這棟大樓位於紐約第三大道的東51街和52街之間。報導表示，消息來源稱，白宮準備採取凍結行動與國家安全有關，原因是紐約市警察局第17警區設在這棟大樓南部的一層，而這個警區負責協助川普大廈的安全保衛。<br />\n<br />\n這棟有58年歷史的大樓的所有權，一旦被美國外國投資委員會從海航手裡移除，將被放入一個信託，任命一名信託管理人，最後可能被出售。<br />\n<br />\n報導表示，海航公司可以到法庭抗辯，這個程序可能會持續數年。而這棟大樓的小股東，一位紐約的房地產投資人則可以在政府任命信託管理人前，有機會尋找另外的合作方。<br />\n<br />\n海航發言人對紐約郵報表示，目前沒有凍結或強迫出售此棟大樓的行動。出於尊重美國外國投資委員會程序的保密性，不會做出更多評論，只是說明這棟大樓位置所涉及的獨特情況在購買大樓時不存在。海航公司在採取慎重步驟解決相關的關切。"},{"pid":"6a140b422c1e6c4df60b495f2d3dfde1d26d7811","tid":773404,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:11:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-trump-administration-to-seize-stake-in-chinese-owned-building-20180809/4520126.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voacantonese.com%2Fa%2Fcantonese-trump-administration-to-seize-stake-in-chinese-owned-building-20180809%2F4520126.html&d=jPMH8utbPTQ9cgNn88%2F0dF0Hwm5JNK6yt%2FgZtp%2B4HOw%3D&h=a22fed22\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.voacantonese.com/a/cantonese-trump-administration-to-seize-stake-in-chinese-owned-building-20180809/4520126.html</a>"},{"pid":"dbc52d022d278be0489500bea8a49b1f3fb90b0f","tid":773404,"uid":13663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/211317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F211317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=21d5fa72&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"53f66067e4b8b39d97558705e7a7bdef2060d740","tid":773404,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:18:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d75a7e34c11423f91486fecb66d6319fe16d4394","tid":773404,"uid":22624,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:33:25.000Z","msg":"侵侵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ecdafadc1c186f6cf929f818bfe1cd28559d5332","tid":773404,"uid":24853,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:40:16.000Z","msg":"侵囝好波<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90904d1f1e3837b173bf7fc11d32b3dc25919893","tid":773404,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"擬"},{"pid":"68523e1bd9bb72e310773c2b5e338fa0364b08be","tid":773404,"uid":66943,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbc52d022d278be0489500bea8a49b1f3fb90b0f","tid":773404,"uid":13663,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T13:13:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/09/211317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F09%2F211317_c5ee0ef1b3d3c76b614b20da3f6f6220.gif&h=21d5fa72&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-09T14:50:06.000Z","msg":"有冇原片<img src=\"/as